description: Partial demolition of existing building at 15 Stockwell Green and redevelopment of site varying in height from 3 to 9 storeys to accommodate a mixed use scheme comprising 290 residential flats, 7,655 sq m of B1 office space with associated caf/service hub (660 sq m), 9 retail units (Class A1/A2/A3/A4/A5) totalling 430 sq m, a management suite, refuse storage areas, basement car park with 131 parking spaces, cycle parking and landscaping plus demolition of former depot and public house at 78 Lingham Street and redevelopment with a 2/3 storey health centre with forecourt delivery and drop off area.
